### 2. TEST AUTORYZACJI
GET {{host}}/api/User
Authorization: Bearer {{myToken}}

### 3. DODANIE OPROGRAMOWANIA
POST {{host}}/api/Software
Authorization: Bearer {{myToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "System ERP",
  "description": "System do zarządzania firmą",
  "currentVersion": "1.0",
  "category": "Finanse"
}

### 4. DODANIE KLIENTA
POST {{host}}/Client/individual
Authorization: Bearer {{myToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jan@kowalski.pl",
  "phone": "123456789",
  "address": "Warszawa",
  "firstName": "Jan",
  "lastName": "Kowalski",
  "pesel": "90010112345"
}

### 5. SPRAWDZENIE AKTUALNEGO PRZYCHODU (Zwróci 0)
GET {{host}}/api/Revenue/current
Authorization: Bearer {{myToken}}

### 6. STWORZENIE KONTRAKTU
POST {{host}}/api/Contract/create-contract
Authorization: Bearer {{myToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": 1,
  "softwareId": 1,
  "softwareVersion": "1.0",
  "startDate": "2026-07-01",
  "endDate": "2026-07-15",
  "price": 10000,
  "yearsOfSupport": 1
}

### 7. OPŁACENIE KONTRAKTU
POST {{host}}/api/Payment
Authorization: Bearer {{myToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contractId": 2,
  "amount": 11000
}

### 8. PRZYCHÓD PO OPŁACENIU (Zwróci 11000)
GET {{host}}/api/Revenue/current
Authorization: Bearer {{myToken}}

### 9. PRZYCHÓD W DOLARACH
GET {{host}}/api/Revenue/current?currency=USD
Authorization: Bearer {{myToken}}

### 10. DODANIE KLIENTA FIRMOWEGO (POST)
# Testujemy dodawanie firmy z numerem KRS
POST {{host}}/Client/company
Authorization: Bearer {{myToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "biuro@superkorpo.pl",
  "phone": "987654321",
  "address": "Kraków, ul. Biznesowa 1",
  "name": "Super Korpo Sp. z o.o.",
  "krs": "0000123456"
}

### 11. EDYCJA KLIENTA INDYWIDUALNEGO (PUT)
PUT {{host}}/Client/1
Authorization: Bearer {{myToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "nowy.jan@kowalski.pl",
  "phone": "111222333",
  "address": "Gdańsk, ul. Morska 2",
  "firstName": "Janusz",
  "lastName": "Kowalski-Nowak"
}

### 12. STWORZENIE KONTRAKTU DLA FIRMY (Oczekujący na płatność)
POST {{host}}/api/Contract/create-contract
Authorization: Bearer {{myToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": 2,
  "softwareId": 1,
  "softwareVersion": "1.0",
  "startDate": "2026-07-01",
  "endDate": "2026-07-15",
  "price": 20000,
  "yearsOfSupport": 2
}

### 13. PRZEWIDYWANY PRZYCHÓD FIRMY (GET)
# Powinno zwrócić sumę: 11000 (zapłacony kontrakt z kroku 7) + 22000 (oczekujący kontrakt z kroku 12). Razem: 33000!
GET {{host}}/api/Revenue/predicted
Authorization: Bearer {{myToken}}

### 14. MIĘKKIE USUNIĘCIE KLIENTA (DELETE)
DELETE {{host}}/Client/1
Authorization: Bearer {{myToken}}

### 15. PRÓBA USUNIĘCIA FIRMY (DELETE - OCZEKIWANY BŁĄD 409)
DELETE {{host}}/Client/2
Authorization: Bearer {{myToken}}